title: Netherlands 2 Year Note Yield
description: Netherlands 2Y Bond Yield was 1.98 percent on Thursday November 10, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Netherlands 2 Year Note Yield reached an all time high of 4.92 in June of 2008. This page includes a chart with historical data for Netherlands 2Y Bond Yield.
